'''艾米莉·霍威尔·华纳'''（{{lang-en|'''Emily Howell Warner'''}}，{{bd|1939年|10月30日|2020年|7月3日|catIdx=Warner}}）出生于[[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]][[丹佛|丹佛]]。是一位美国民航[[飞行员|飞行员]]，是美国[[航空公司|航空公司]]第一位女性[[機長|機長]]。<ref name="National Aviation HoF">{{cite web | url=http://nationalaviation.org/2013/12/national-aviation-hall-of-fame-reveals-names-of-class-of-2014-at-wright-brothers-anniversary-dinner/ | title=National Aviation Hall of Fame reveals names of "Class of 2014" at Wright Brothers Anniversary dinner | publisher=National Aviation Hall of Fame | date=2013-12-17 | access-date=2016-07-14 | archive-date=2014-06-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611173143/http://nationalaviation.org/2013/12/national-aviation-hall-of-fame-reveals-names-of-class-of-2014-at-wright-brothers-anniversary-dinner/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>

1973年，华纳成为1934年{{le|海伦·里奇|Helen Richey}}被聘为副驾驶后的第一位被美国航空公司计划录用的女飞行员。<ref name="SIU Press">{{cite book | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7ccymjJZxLcC | title=The American Aviation Experience: A History | publisher=Southern Illinois University Press | author=Brady, Tim | year=2000 | isbn=9780809323715 | access-date=2016-07-14 | archive-date=2020-08-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813170636/https://books.google.com/books?id=7ccymjJZxLcC | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Douglas">{{cite book | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=c89LN66l9M4C | title=American Women and Flight Since 1940 | publisher=University Press of Kentucky | author=Douglas, Deborah G. | year=2004 | isbn=9780813126258 | access-date=2016-07-14 | archive-date=2020-08-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813165631/https://books.google.com/books?id=c89LN66l9M4C | dead-url=no }}</ref>1976年华纳成为美国航空公司第一位女[[机长|机长]]。<ref name="Smithsonian">{{cite web | url=http://airandspace.si.edu/explore-and-learn/topics/women-in-aviation/Warner.cfm | title=Women in Aviation and Space History, Emily Howell Warner | publisher=Smithsonian National Air and Space Museum | work=America by Air | author1=Cochrane, D. | author2=Ramirez, P. | access-date=2016-07-14 | archive-date=2015-03-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150308042743/http://airandspace.si.edu/explore-and-learn/topics/women-in-aviation/Warner.cfm | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Princeton">{{cite book | url=http://press.princeton.edu/titles/9542.html | title=The 1970s: A New Global History from Civil Rights to Economic Inequality | publisher=Princeton University Press | author=Borstelmann, Thomas | year=2011 | isbn=9781400839704 | access-date=2016-07-14 | archive-date=2019-03-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329163953/https://press.princeton.edu/titles/9542.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>她的职业生涯中获得很多荣誉，其中包括入选{{le|国家航空名人堂|National Aviation Hall of Fame}}和[[国家女性名人堂|国家女性名人堂]]。<ref name="AP 2002">{{cite news | url=http://www.apnewsarchive.com/2002/1st-Female-Makes-Hall-of-Fame/id-92b9a722f52eeb2ae1b2e20929df0e2f | title=1st Female Makes Hall of Fame | work=Associated Press | date=2002-10-05 | author=Dobbin, Ben | accessdate=2016-07-14 | archive-date=2018-04-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180413194556/http://www.apnewsarchive.com/2002/1st-Female-Makes-Hall-of-Fame/id-92b9a722f52eeb2ae1b2e20929df0e2f | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NWHF">{{cite web|url=https://www.greatwomen.org/women-of-the-hall/search-the-hall/details/2/193-Warner |title=Emily Howell Warner |publisher=National Women's Hall of Fame |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004105340/http://www.greatwomen.org/women-of-the-hall/search-the-hall/details/2/193-Warner |archivedate=2013-10-04 }}</ref>她的飞行员的制服在[[史密森尼学会|史密森尼]][[美国国家航空航天博物馆|国家航空航天博物馆]]中展出。<ref name="AOPA">{{cite news | url=https://www.aopa.org/Pilot-Resources/Aviation-Resources-for-Youth/AOPA-AV8RS/AV8RS-Newsletter/AV8RS-Articles/2014/February/Emily-Howell-Warner.aspx | title=Howell-Warner: 1st woman to be hired as a pilot by major U.S. airline | work=AV8TR Newsletter | date=2014-01-17 | agency=Aircraft Owners and Pilots Association | accessdate=2016-07-14 | archive-date=2014-10-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141012160845/https://www.aopa.org/Pilot-Resources/Aviation-Resources-for-Youth/AOPA-AV8RS/AV8RS-Newsletter/AV8RS-Articles/2014/February/Emily-Howell-Warner.aspx | dead-url=no }}</ref>华纳还在科罗拉多州[[丹佛|丹佛]]的一个飞行学校担任主管。她也是一名飞行教练并是[[美国联邦航空管理局|美国联邦航空管理局]]指定的持有多个评级的考官。<ref name="National Aviation HoF" />她的职业生涯拥有超过21,000小时飞行经验和进行了超过3000次的设施检查和评估。<ref name="National Aviation HoF" /><ref name="Air Line Pilot">{{cite news|url=http://cf.alpa.org/internet/alp/2000/jun00p29.htm |title=Emily Warner, The First Female Pilot Member of the Air Line Pilots Association |work=Air Line Pilot |date=June–July 2000 |author1=Wise, Rick |author2=Witvliet, Jolanda |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140315033626/http://cf.alpa.org/internet/alp/2000/jun00p29.htm |archivedate=2014-03-15 }}</ref>

